# Cloning a specific GHC Version

List tags to see all tags: 

    list tag 

Clone specific version

    git clone --recursive --branch <TAG> https://gitlab.haskell.org/ghc/ghc <DIRECTORY>
    cd <DIRECTORY>
    switchghc <x.y.z>     # switch to a version lower than the specific version 
    hadrian full